    "Even an expert cannot explain how they produced their outputs.",
    "Consequently, their reliability always seems to be in question.",
    "As AI develops, its quality in general is likely to improve, but that does not mean it has improved in whatever application is being deployed.",
    "Educational institutions typically have a long lead-in time, so many instructors may find themselves using elderly AI.",
